    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Black July Commemoration in University",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna University Students' Union celebrated Black July Memorial Day at the obelisk located at the main entrance of Jaffna University this morning.",
        "On this occasion, students hoisted a black flag on the main flagpole of Jaffna University near the main entrance of the university and flew it at half-mast.",
        "After this, the students lit a flame and paid floral tributes to the Black July statue in the main obelisk of the university.",
        "Also there was a commemoration of the injustices done to Tamils \u200b\u200bduring the Black July Week of 1983."
      ],
